Asda Shuffles Its Management in Competitive Push, Times Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-04-18T01:27:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/asda-shuffles-its-management-in-competitive-push-times-reports.html
Wal-Mart Stores Inc. (WMT) ’s U.K.
supermarket chain, Asda, has shaken up its management in recent
weeks as it aims to increase its share of the country’s market,
the London-based Times reported, citing an internal company
document. One of the new appointments, Arnu Misra, who was most
recently employed by Canadian chain Loblaw Cos. Ltd., will carry
out a comprehensive review of Asda’s “new business
opportunity,” the newspaper said.    Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
